*Portuguese: [[psicótico]] ''m'', [[psicopático]] ''m''

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# {{cattag|pejorative|slang}} A [[person]] who is [[psychotic]] or otherwise [[insane]].
#:''The loony bin up on the hill is full of '''psychos'''.''
# {{cattag|pejorative|slang}} A [[person]] who acts in a [[bizarre]] or [[dangerous]] manner.
#:''She complained that he was a '''psycho''' for driving at such a high speed in heavy traffic.''''Zoe Genova.''

